Package group.gan.mvc.model.game

Interface GameModel

All Known Implementing Classes:
GameModelImpl
public interface GameModel
GameModel is used to save some data in the game and verify the state of the game itself. Since our team does not implement the advanced function of saving games. Therefore, the functions of GameModel in this project are not rich. However, it has the implementation of advanced functions with reserved interfaces. (our group didn't have to implement it)
